1:27:20.490 --> 1:27:22.030
<i>-Yeah, I'm ready-</i>
-All right.

1:27:22.150 --> 1:27:23.910
<i>Looking forward to walking up to you</i>
<i>four days ago</i>

1:27:24.030 --> 1:27:25.160
<i>and blowing your mind, though-</i>

1:27:25.280 --> 1:27:26.660
Well, if that happens,
maybe you can tell me

1:27:26.780 --> 1:27:28.120
