-Get me out of here!
-All right. All right.

1:35:03.620 --> 1:35:05.370
Get me out of here!

1:35:05.700 --> 1:35:09.250
It's all right. It's okay. It's okay.

1:35:10.920 --> 1:35:13.710
-Get me out of here.
-All right, let me get your feet.

1:35:13.830 --> 1:35:16.550
It's all right. It's all right. It's all right.

1:35:19.300 --> 1:35:21.680
Hey, look at me. Look at me.

1:35:21.800 --> 1:35:24.090
I'm gonna get you out of here, okay?

1:35:24.220 --> 1:35:25.680
All right.

