1:37:46.030 --> 1:37:49.200
The blue and white one. Anything.
It's just...

1:37:49.320 --> 1:37:50.320
Just trust me.

1:37:50.450 --> 1:37:54.580
The victim wore a dress like that
and it wouldn't be good.

1:37:56.160 --> 1:37:57.920
-Okay.
-Trust me.

1:37:58.290 --> 1:38:02.840
All right, I'll go change. I'll be right out.

1:38:13.310 --> 1:38:15.100
Stop right there! Don't move!

1:38:15.220 --> 1:38:17.350
Don't move. I'm calling the police.

1:38:17.600 --> 1:38:19.230
-I am the police.
-No, you're not.

1:38:19.350 --> 1:38:20.650
-Yes, I am.
-No, you're not!

1:38:20.770 --> 1:38:23.480
You didn't ask me any questions.
You didn't take a statement.

1:38:23.610 --> 1:38:26.940
And you knew where my house was,
what's in my closet.

1:38:27.320 --> 1:38:31.200
-Who are you?
-I'm Doug Carlin. I'm an ATF agent.

1:38:31.320 --> 1:38:34.030
I'm part of a special surveillance unit
that's been tracking the man

1:38:34.120 --> 1:38:35.830
-who was trying to kill you.
-How do I know that?

1:38:35.950 --> 1:38:37.540
I had a hood over my head.
You could be him.

1:38:37.660 --> 1:38:38.660
Just think about it, Claire.

1:38:38.790 --> 1:38:40.460
Look at my face.
You scratched the man's face.

1:38:40.580 --> 1:38:42.290
Do I have a scratch on my face?

1:38:42.420 --> 1:38:46.260
-You scratched him, didn't you?
-Get on the floor.

1:38:47.380 --> 1:38:48.970
Now! Get on the floor!

1:38:52.260 --> 1:38:53.800
All the way!

1:38:56.970 --> 1:38:59.060
ATF New Orleans, Agent Donnelly.

1:38:59.190 --> 1:39:03.310
Yes, is there an Agent Douglas Carlin
working out of that branch?

1:39:03.440 --> 1:39:05.900
<i>Yes, there is,</i>
<i>but he's not here right now-</i>

1:39:06.400 --> 1:39:08.030
Would you like to leave a message?

1:39:08.150 --> 1:39:10.150
Can you describe him for me, please?

1:39:10.280 --> 1:39:12.110
How tall, skin colour.

1:39:12.910 --> 1:39:17.790
I don't know.
He's 6'3", black, not bad-looking.

1:39:20.660 --> 1:39:23.170
Okay, have him call me back

1:39:23.290 --> 1:39:26.750
at 877-504-8423.

