Okay, wait. My phone pad's empty.

1:39:28.590 --> 1:39:29.920
All right, got it.

1:39:31.550 --> 1:39:32.590
Hello?

1:39:37.770 --> 1:39:38.930
Get up.

1:39:46.360 --> 1:39:48.530
Are you gonna tell me the truth?

1:39:48.650 --> 1:39:51.780
Are you gonna tell me why you're here,
why this is happening

1:39:51.900 --> 1:39:54.530
and none of it makes sense?
None of it.

1:39:56.240 --> 1:39:59.040
What if you had to tell someone
the most important thing in the world,

1:39:59.160 --> 1:40:01.370
but you knew they'd never believe you?

1:40:03.250 --> 1:40:04.500
What would you do?

1:40:05.580 --> 1:40:06.670
I'd try.

1:40:07.750 --> 1:40:10.550
You never know
what someone might believe.

1:40:16.720 --> 1:40:21.270
I don't understand what's...
What's happening.

1:40:45.750 --> 1:40:47.540
I gotta hurry up and get down there.

1:40:47.670 --> 1:40:49.590
Why are you the only one
who can stop him?

1:40:49.550 --> 1:40:50.340
Why are you the only one
who can stop him?

